title: Live Outside The Lines of the Mission District at Highpoint Terrace!!!
posting_body: ['HIGHPOINT TERRACE CONDOMINIUMS', 'Built on a terraced acre, Highpoint consists of 48 condominiums ranging from 1,000 to 2,500 square feet, designed to be open and filled with natural light.', 'These homes offer plenty of windows, high ceilings, fireplaces, mixtures of hardwood and modern flooring, and balconies with a panoramic view of San Francisco Bay.', 'Residents have access to a state-of-the-art clubhouse, arcade-style game room, media room, fitness center, and bay view terrace.', 'Located directly in front of McLaren Park, a 312-acre park that features many family activities and more than 7 miles of walking trails.', 'Highpoint combines two desired qualities rarely found together in the city, spacious living surrounded by the beauty of nature.', 'CONDOMINIUM FEATURES', 'In-unit Washer/Dryer', 'Wood and Plank Style Flooring', 'Bay Views from every Balcony', 'Enlarged Patios', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Dual Sink Master Bathroom', 'Electric Fireplace', 'Granite Countertops', 'Track Lighting', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'Controlled building access', 'Remote access parking garage', 'Sky Deck', 'Elevators', 'Clubhouse', 'Pool table', 'Mini Arcade', 'Fitness Center', 'On-site Maintenance', 'On-site Management', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'APPLY TODAY', 'Highpoint Terrace', 'Leasing Office', '1888 Geneva Ave,', 'San Francisco, CA 94134', 'Office:', 'show contact info', '<URL>', '#0216']
